{"tid":339188,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［媽媽是小學四年生］10歲女童因姦成孕，印法院禁墜胎","createTime":"2017-07-28T23:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T17:43:06.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"238e266bf1af57b16a4668265c338fef38c91624","tid":339188,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T23:07:16.000Z","msg":"印度一名10歲女童被舅舅強姦後懷孕，現時胎兒已6個月大，但女童年紀太小，法院徵詢醫療專家意見後，裁定她不能墮胎。<br />\n該名女孩感到胃痛，於是告訴父母，才揭發她曾遭舅舅強姦6次，疑犯被捕。女孩家人其後向當地地區法院申請批准女兒墮胎。<br />\n<br />\n法庭詢問過8名醫療專家意見後，裁定女童現階段不能墮胎。醫療專家指，由於女孩年紀太小不適合停止懷孕，但胎兒已6個月大，懷孕過程容易引起併發症，分娩也會對母嬰構成危險，甚至剖腹產也有重大風險。專家又指，即使能順利誕下嬰兒，他出世後亦可能有危及生命的併發症，包括貧血和高血壓等。<br />\n<br />\n根據印度法例，女性懷孕20周以上就不能墮胎，除非證明胎兒會危害母親性命或有遺傳問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170722/s00005/1500706500539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170722%2Fs00005%2F1500706500539&d=O8Th30%2F6NwmgSi%2BxoenX2mMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ad643964\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170722%2Fs00005%2F1500706500539&h=b970ba28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170722/s00005/1500706500539</a>"},{"pid":"b596989b8ca1b1b1b9f4eb654d64466652f80f23","tid":339188,"uid":55386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T01:28:57.000Z","msg":"個女竟然冇罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00df68010a4d0f5eba683f8297924edfa863949","tid":339188,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f4a78b4627495cc678dedfbb1ef4612e3e94a4","tid":339188,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"